quran[17]{c,v,t}:
  36,51,"wnufikh fi \"alqrn\" alnfkht althanyt, fturadd arwahhm 'iilaa ajsadhm, fa'iidha hum min qbwrhm yakhrujun 'iilaa rabihim sraeana"
  36,52,"qal almukadhibun balbeth nadmyn: ya hlakna man 'ukhrijna min qbwrna? fyjabwn wyqal lhm: hdha maa waead bih alrhmn, wakhbr eanh almursalun alsadqwn"
  36,53,"ma kan albaeth min alqubur 'iilaa natijat nafkhat wahidat fi \"alqrn\", fa'iidha jmye alkhalq ladayna mathlwn llhsab waljza'"
  36,54,"fy dhlk alyawm ytm alhisab baledl, fala tuzlm nafs shyyana bnqs hsnatha 'aw ziadat syyatha, wala tujzwn 'iilaa bima kuntum temlwnh fi aldnya"
  36,55,'in 'ahl aljanat fi dhalik alyawm mshghwlwn ean ghyrhm bi'anwae alnaeim alty ytfkhwn bha
  36,56,"hm wa'azwajihim mtnemwn baljlws ealaa alasrrat almzyant, taht alzilal alwarft"
  36,57,"lhm fi aljanat 'anwae alfwakh alldhydht, walahum kl ma yatlubun min 'anwae alneym"
  36,58,"wlhm naeim akhar 'akbar hin yukalimuhum rbhm, alrahim bihim bialsalam elyhm. waeind dhlk tahsul lahum alsalamat alttamat min jmye alwjwh"
  36,59,"wyqal llkfar fi dhalik alywm: tmyazu ean almwmnyn, wanfslu enhm"
  36,60,"wyqwl allah lahum twbykhana wtdhkyrana: 'alam awskm ealaa alsnt rusuli 'an laa taebuduu alshaytan wala ttyewh? 'iinah lakum eaduun zahir aledawt"
  36,61,"wamrtkm bebadty whdy, febadty wtaety wmesyt alshaytan hi aldiyn alqwym almawsil lmrdaty wjnnaty"
  36,62,"wlqd adll alshaytan ean alhaqu minkum khlqana kthyrana, 'afama kan lakum eaql -ayha almshrkwn- yanhakum ean atbaeh?"
  36,63,hdhh jahanam alati kuntum tueadun biha fi aldunya ealaa kfrkm biallah wtkdhybkm rslh
  36,64,adkhlwha alyawm wqasu hrraha; bsbb kfrkm
  36,65,"alyawm natbae ealaa afwah almushrikin fala yntqwn, wtukllimna 'aydihim bima btsht bh, watashhad 'arjuluhum bima saeat 'iilayh fi aldnya, wksbt min alatham"
  36,66,"wlw nasha' latamasna ealaa 'aeyunuhum bi'ana nudhhb absarhm, kama khtmna ealaa afwahhm, fbadaru 'iilaa alsirat lyjwzwh, fkyf yatahaqaq lahum dhlk waqad tumist absarhm?"
  36,67,"wlw shina laghayarna khalaqahum waqednahm fi amaknhm, fala yastatieun 'an yamdu amamhm, wala yrjeu wra'hm"